dcterms:description: A real side scan sonar dataset consisting of 220 scans of 14 distinct shipwreck sites collected with an AUV in Thunder Bay National Marine Sanctuary (TBNMS), which includes detailed and high-resolution labels generated by an expert marine archaeologist.
dcterms:title: TBNMS Dataset (Thunder Bay National Marine Sanctuary Dataset)

dcterms:description: A synthetic dataset generated by the authors using their own methods to create side scan sonar images for training purposes.
dcterms:title: Synthetic Dataset
